A BILL TO BE ENTITLED
AN ACT
1 To amend Article 1 of Chapter 1 of Title 20 of the Official Code of Georgia Annotated,
2 relating to general provisions relative to education, so as to require employers of public
3 school teachers and employees and postsecondary employees to provide leaves of absence
4 for the donation of bone marrow and organs; to provide for standards and conditions for
5 granting such leaves of absence; to prohibit waivers of such leaves of absence; to provide for
6 definitions; to provide for a short title; to provide for related matters; to repeal conflicting
7 laws; and for other purposes.
8 BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF GEORGIA:
9 SECTION 1.
10 This Act shall be known and may be cited as the "Georgia Supporting Living Donor
11 Educators Act."
12 SECTION 2.
13 Article 1 of Chapter 1 of Title 20 of the Official Code of Georgia Annotated, relating to
14 general provisions relative to education, is amended by adding a new Code section to read
15 as follows:
